1812
02:29:57,200 --> 02:30:03,920
But rarer still, a mind with\h
memories and experiences will occur.

1813
02:30:03,920 --> 02:30:09,720
These ethereal minds are known as Boltzmann\h
Brains and are extremely rare events.\h

1814
02:30:09,720 --> 02:30:16,319
But with infinite time available they\h
will appear again and again and again.\h

1815
02:30:16,319 --> 02:30:21,479
And over and over again, even your exact\h
consciousness will pop into existence.\h

1816
02:30:21,479 --> 02:30:25,439
Your consciousness with all of\h
your memories and experiences.

1817
02:30:25,439 --> 02:30:28,399
An infinite number of times.

1818
02:30:29,600 --> 02:30:32,000
Picking one of these at random, you are much\h\h

1819
02:30:32,000 --> 02:30:36,920
more likely to be a Boltzmann’s\h
Brain in a cold, dead universe,\h

1820
02:30:36,920 --> 02:30:43,240
Than a physical, fleshy human\h
enjoying a green, ripe apple.

1821
02:30:43,240 --> 02:30:50,080
You – the mind watching this video – temporary.
Your existence simply a fluctuation,\h\h

