1825
02:31:09,160 --> 02:31:10,479
Yes.

1826
02:31:10,479 --> 02:31:14,679
At least for now.

1827
02:31:14,680 --> 02:31:19,680
And so for one final time your\h
eyes settle on the solitary apple.\h

1828
02:31:19,680 --> 02:31:25,120
The apple that sent you on this journey\h
